info.description:
===========
 pyducteev
===========
---------------------------
 A Producteev_ API library
---------------------------

pyducteev is a library to manage tasks and workspaces on Producteev_.
It is not in a usable state, however it is under very active
development.

In order to use it in your application, you will need an API key, which
you can find more about here_.

.. _Producteev: http://www.producteev.com/
.. _here: http://code.google.com/p/producteev-api/
